content: Watch out for a few Grasshopper Guai trapped in some of the larger cocoons as you approach a large hole in the middle of the path with an archer on the far side. There's actually a wooden ledge near here that offers one of two ways to drop down to a lower level, but we'll backtrack to this spot later since it's a lengthy and one-way trip.
